Bootstrap: library
From: debian:10

%post
apt-get update
apt-get install -y gcc g++ libgomp1 git git-lfs
git lfs install
mkdir ${SINGULARITY_ROOTFS}/MyRoot
cd ${SINGULARITY_ROOTFS}/MyRoot
git lfs clone https://github.com/Alereds/CapriHPC.git
cd CapriHPC
g++ -fopenmp CAPRIComputeNormals.cpp -o CAPRIComputeNormals.o

%runscript
cd ${SINGULARITY_ROOTFS}/MyRoot/CapriHPC
./CAPRIComputeNormals.o

%labels
Author Alessandro Rossi
Version 1.0

%help
This is a simple example of Singularity container. The container
is based on Debian 10 and it contains a C++ program